Aurobindo Reports First-Quarter Loss on Bond Payments

-- B y   R u t h   D a v i d
-- 
2011-08-08T03:46:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-08/aurobindo-reports-first-quarter-loss-on-bond-payments-correct-.html
(Corrects net income figure in the story moved on Aug. 6
to reflect loss.)  Aurobindo Pharma Ltd. (ARBP)  today reported
a loss of 1.23 billion rupees ($27.3 million) in the quarter
ended June 30 after the company redeemed its foreign currency
convertible bonds worth $139.2 million.  For Related News and Information:  To contact the reporter on this story:
